my then boss said, Martin, take a seat.

36
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,600
Hold your horses.

37
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:46,320
And instead of me going through the slides, he showed the perplex audience one sketch.

38
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,960
One visual metaphor.

39
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,160
And it was this one.

40
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:52,480
It was a fortress built on sand.

41
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:58,640
