49
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:24,000
And I could show finally my slide with that analysis.

50
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:30,560
But this leading with a visual metaphor really changed the dynamics of the conversation.

51
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,160
It was much more collaborative.

52
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:36,960
First, you overview with this visual metaphor and then the details on demand.

53
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:39,920
And I realized it's all about a conversation.

54
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,280
It's much better this way.

55
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:44,480
When you first show overview with the help of a metaphor that by the way,

